{"title":"itertools模块中实用函数","slug":"2019-01-26-itertools","date":"2019-01-26T14:11:07.000Z","updated":"2019-01-28T03:31:57.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/2019-01-26-itertools.json","photos":[],"link":"","excerpt":null,"covers":null,"content":"<ul>\n<li><p><code>islice</code>可以实现对迭代器和生成器的切片操作，但会消耗掉提供的迭代器中的数据。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">islice(iterable,stop)</span><br><span class=\"line\">islice(iterable,start,stop[,step])</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p><code>dropwhile</code>会抛弃满足条件的元素，返回从不满足条件的第一个元素开始到迭代结束的所有元素。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">dropwhile(predicate,iterable)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p><code>permutations</code>生成全排列，可指定需要的元素数目</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">permutations(iterable[,r])</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p><code>combinatinos</code>生成全组合</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">combinations(iterable,r)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p><code>zip_longest</code>同时迭代多个序列，并以最长的序列作为结束标准，不够的补<code>fillvalue</code></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">zip_longest(iter1,[...],[fillvalue=<span class=\"keyword\">None</span>])</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p><code>chain</code>对多个容器进行迭代</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">chain(*iterables)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n</ul>\n","categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"python","slug":"python","count":7,"path":"api/tags/python.json"}]}